fu.gps

Class GPSDecoder

  • java.lang.Object
    • fu.gps.GPSDecoder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.EventListener, javax.comm.SerialPortEventListener

    public class GPSDecoder
extends java.lang.Object
implements javax.comm.SerialPortEventListener
    The GPSDecoder class reads the nmea datastream generated by a GPSDecoder.

    The class reads from the specified comport (or Com1 if no comport was specified) and stores the data available.
